snippet.title: That's Amazing
snippet.description:
Welcome to That's Amazing! We are two brothers, Tommy and Matthew, who love to make incredible trick shots, and our siblings do, too!  We hope you like our videos, and if you do, please subscribe!

That's Amazing Shorts: www.youtube.com/c/thatsamazingshorts.com

Get some merch here!  https://www.thatsamazingshop.com
